Global Decentralized Servo Drives Market Insights
Decentralized Servo Drives Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.7 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Decentralized Servo Drives Market Overview
The decentralized servo drives market was valued at USD 20.7 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 42.03 billion by 2031, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 10.73% from 2024 to 2031. This growth is driven by advancements in industrial automation, the integration of Internet of Things (IoT) technologies, and the increasing demand for energy-efficient solutions across various industries. Decentralized servo drives offer enhanced performance, flexibility, and cost-effectiveness, making them a preferred choice in sectors such as manufacturing, automotive, and robotics.

